metadata.description: Manchester United vs Tottenham Hotspur match result for 7 February 2026

outcome_space.description: Manchester United vs Tottenham Hotspur Premier League match result (7 February 2026)

base_case.condition: What is the full-time result of {outcome}?
base_case.fsp_resolution: FSP=1.0 if Manchester United wins (home victory), FSP=0.5 if the match ends in a draw or is cancelled/abandoned with no official result adjudicated, FSP=0.0 if Tottenham Hotspur wins (away victory). Result is determined by the final score at full-time (90 minutes + stoppage time). Data sources: Primary <https://www.premierleague.com/en/match/2562142/manchester-united-vs-tottenham-hotspur/overview>; Secondary <https://www.espn.com/soccer/report/_/gameId/740843>.

edge_cases.condition: Match is postponed, abandoned, or cancelled with no official result adjudicated
edge_cases.fsp_resolution: FSP=0.5 (evaluates to UNRESOLVED) - there is no formally adjudicated match result. Data sources: Primary <https://www.premierleague.com/en/match/2562142/manchester-united-vs-tottenham-hotspur/overview>; Secondary <https://www.espn.com/soccer/report/_/gameId/740843>.

edge_cases.condition: Official result cannot be verified from primary or secondary data sources within 48 hours after scheduled kick-off
edge_cases.fsp_resolution: FSP=0.5 (evaluates to UNRESOLVED) - oracle cannot verify official match result from specified data sources within the required timeframe.

outcome_point.outcome: Manchester United vs Tottenham Hotspur on 7 February 2026
